h","format-standard","hentry","category-wisdom-al-hikmah","tag-abu-bakr","tag-caliphs-khulafah","tag-community-jamaah","tag-companions-sahaba","tag-death-mawt","tag-following-al-itibaa","tag-leadership-imamah","tag-manners-adab","tag-prophetic-biography-seerah-nabawiyya","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-sunnah","tag-umar-ibn-al-khattab"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-2SF","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":11080,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/ali-best-ummah-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":11077,"position":0},"title":"Ali on Caliphs: Best companions are Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you about the best of this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr and Umar.\" Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 878 Grade\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062c\u064f\u062d\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34420,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/09\/30\/uhud-trembles-khulafa\/","url_meta":{"origin":11077,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Uhud trembles for Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was climbing Mount Uhud with Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman when it began to quake because of them. The Prophet said, \u201cBe still, Uhud! It is but a Prophet, a truthful man, and two martyrs upon you!\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33693,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/09\/fadl-abu-bakr-umar-ammar\/","url_meta":{"origin":11077,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Virtues of Abu Bakr, Umar, \u2018Ammar, and Ibn Mas\u2019ud","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFollow these two men from my companions after me, Abu Bakr and Umar. Accept the guidance of \u2018Ammar, and take the advice of Ibn Mas\u2019ud.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3805 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38968,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/03\/02\/ali-testifies-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":11077,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Ali testifies for Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not inform you of the best from this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr, and the best after him is Umar. Then, Allah will place goodness wherever He wishes.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 922 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43677,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/abu-bakr-umar-honored-ummah\/","url_meta":{"origin":11077,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Abu Bakr and Umar honored in Ummah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Hantab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saw Abu Bakr and Umar, saying, \u201cThese two are the hearing and the sight.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3671 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani Imam al-Qari commented, \u201cMeaning, their two souls are one to the extent they are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-sireen-degrades-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":11077,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Sireen on Sahaba: Whoever degrades Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ayyub reported: Muhammad ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI suspect that a man who denigrates Abu Bakr and Umar does not love the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3685 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11077","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11077"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11077\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11077"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=11077"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=11077"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}